    public class FlowModEntryTable
extends java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap<java.lang.String,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,org.openflow.protocol.OFFlowMod>>
    This table is of type ConcurrentHashMap<String, Map<String, OFFlowMod>>. The first key (String) is DPID, and the second key (String) is the name of the flow mod (for example, "flow-mod-1").
